               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mäṣḥafä ʾardǝʾǝt “Book of the Disciples” [The long version beginning with በስመ፡“… ነገረ፡ ዘ፲ወ፪አርድእት… ] (fols. 7ra-65va)&#xD;
II) Ṣälotä śǝryätä ḫaṭiʾat “Prayer of Absolution of Sins” (fols. 65vb-79ra)&#xD;
III) Ṣälot zä-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝnä Maryam bä-Däbrä Golgota, Prayer of Our Lady Mary on Mount Golgotha on the 21st of Säne (fols. 79rb-97rb)&#xD;
IV) Tǝmhǝrtä ḫǝbuʾat “Teaching of Mysteries” (fols. 97va-103vb)&#xD;
V) ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer zä-bǝrhanat ʾǝgziʾabǝḥer zä-śǝlṭanat... “God of Lights, God of Powers...” (fols. 103vc-106vb) (cp. ChRep no. 363)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-10.</summary>
